Every major news and opinion outlet has had something to say about political correctness, from the Atlantic to the New York Times to Reason Magazine to Cosmo.
The political correctness hypothesis appears to be jumping the shark already, if that shark hasn’t already been jumped.
It’s easy to cast off those who reject political correctness as brutes and bullies, just as it’s easy to cast off PC defenders as sissies and snowflakes.
